mbelib-rs Licensing
===================

This crate is distributed under the GNU General Public License, version 2
or (at your option) any later version (GPL-2.0-or-later). This matches the
workspace-wide license choice for the kenwood project.

It is a Rust port of code from two upstream C projects authored by szechyjs,
both originally published under the ISC license. ISC permits redistribution
under more restrictive terms, so those portions are redistributed in this
crate under GPL-2.0-or-later, with the original ISC copyright notices
retained for attribution as ISC requires.

This is the same relicensing pathway that arancormonk used in mbelib-neo
(https://github.com/arancormonk/mbelib-neo) — taking the ISC mbelib code
and redistributing the combined work under GPL-2.0-or-later.

